DOC.brief_summary: This study is conducted in Europe. The aim of this observational study is to observe and investigate the process of switching from premixed human insulin 30/70 (BHI 30) to biphasic insulin aspart 30/70 (BIAsp 30) in an outpatient setting.
DOC.brief_title: Switch From Premixed Human Insulin to Biphasic Insulin Aspart in the Netherlands
DOC.mesh_term: Insulin degludec, insulin aspart drug combination
Insulin aspart, insulin aspart protamine drug combination 30:70
DOC.criteria: Type 2 diabetic subjects treated with BHI 30
